{"tid":310394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做過扁桃腺切除手術請入!","createTime":"2017-07-05T18:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T00:40:54.000Z","uid":126929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8ebc26f0d801868c3ca9e6c59a8e3034fa1c4994","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺成日都發炎 唔會嚴重到發燒 <br />\n但係喉嚨會好痕 痕到訓唔到 小小痛 <br />\n扁桃腺會多左結石<br />\n結石問題係細細粒 可能係因為我差唔多日日清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始發現既時候係好大粒 <br />\n有口臭問題 都幾嚴重 有時唔開口 呼吸都會有臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想切左個扁桃腺去 想問下做呢個手術大概要幾錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋想知大家情況係咪差唔多？<br />\n窮撚要靠自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1100bd968faaa3008279dc9d4cec6ca8239ece4","tid":310394,"uid":80816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T21:38:06.000Z","msg":"公立醫院好平 不過唔知等幾耐<br />\n醫生覺得你情況緊急就超快<br />\n我個次一見醫生就安排我十幾日後去切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似加加埋埋幾百蚊左右"},{"pid":"03874cece0492e8e97439349fb3235f57fa31af6","tid":310394,"uid":66779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T21:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公立醫院好平 不過唔知等幾耐<br />\n醫生覺得你情況緊急就超快<br />\n我個次一見醫生就安排我十幾日後去切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似加加埋埋幾百蚊左右</blockquote><br />\n切完之後有冇咩特別？<br />\n<br />\n啲結石係幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cb88610bbe4562abacec80970116573cee4aa3","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478ca774e386762b277f3a668a97c71d8fa95e60","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公立醫院好平 不過唔知等幾耐<br />\n醫生覺得你情況緊急就超快<br />\n我個次一見醫生就安排我十幾日後去切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似加加埋埋幾百蚊左右</blockquote><br />\n我覺得自己應該唔係緊急 扁桃腺又唔係特別大 正常size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0481e1834eea93f5cee31798b176513e2c13752f","tid":310394,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T04:28:02.000Z","msg":"你預私家4萬幾啦, 冇保險就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5364b0365fd61ed0867433debba65382576e8aa","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T05:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你預私家4萬幾啦, 冇保險就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求介紹醫生"},{"pid":"cd25e9a1f39a7a4511e1ee4bc67ff3c1f6cd6138","tid":310394,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你預私家4萬幾啦, 冇保險就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求介紹醫生</blockquote><br />\n費時比人話打手"},{"pid":"8c6bacdb9bfc195223128801ee8bb47a35b8bac4","tid":310394,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"小學3年級係廣華醫院做過"},{"pid":"a440a58dbb49983a87aa01a900092d65a653be7f","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你預私家4萬幾啦, 冇保險就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求介紹醫生</blockquote><br />\n費時比人話打手</blockquote><br />\n巴打留TG得唔得"},{"pid":"4d487cb9c5c459bdb36bcfc55114df87ecf1f149","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:09:02.000Z","msg":