55732da8b9889838c90550270e4381d13003712","tid":310394,"uid":89334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我切左5，6年 切完之後好似成個人都好口乾咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當時咩原因切？</blockquote><br />\n個陣晚晚鼻鼾聲超大 個人訓極唔夠咁<br />\n後來一次感冒睇醫生 順便問埋<br />\n醫生話我天生扁桃腺過大 <br />\n話如果個人反轉訓<br />\n可能會有睡眠窒塞症 （本身鼻敏感）<br />\n所以就切左<br />\n不過切完 之後我而家日日訓勁小個人都好精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7acadca39afd8ba1a22b9985e47992664e0cd367","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:06:12.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打近呢幾年割可以分享下手術費用幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋救介紹醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5a5b953a6e8cfdfe64bc44218d3092dde7b9f2","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打近呢幾年割可以分享下手術費用幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋求介紹醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"57e0831c87445856d56ea302a1945c9587ff4022","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceecd4d5e7d6c0032ecd7333a86b1d0031449b7e","tid":310394,"uid":124557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"啲結石點清?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdb8865eb7a1b987542abfdd31076a97a7120c1","tid":310394,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:09:41.000Z","msg":"好慘"},{"pid":"5f077a8dbc84d94465afcd36cce1bdb163592df5","tid":310394,"uid":108311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"Push <br />\n通常要排幾耐同幾錢？"},{"pid":"6e8bfb2ba4c2b72263a17fbc07f644a11ce2a8d7","tid":310394,"uid":126929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲結石點清?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對鏡用棉花棒壓出黎"}]}